pany of men, Msb)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "walked, marched,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "went on foot,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ilayohi", "text_ar": "اـِلَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (S, K;) and [generally]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "did so by little and little;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(accord. to an explanation of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHofN", "text_ar": "زَحْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "crept,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "crawled, along;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "went,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "walked, leisurely,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gently:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tzH~f A_ilayohi", "text_ar": "تزحّف اـِلَيْهِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AzdHf", "text_ar": "ازدحف", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tm$~Y", "text_ar": "تمشّى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he walked"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with slow steps,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heavily, with an effort, to him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TK:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mi$oyapu zaHafaAnK", "text_ar": "مِشْيَةُ زَحَفَانٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a gait in which is a heaviness of motion."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) One says of a child, before he walks, (S, Msb, K,) or before he stands, (T, TA,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yazoHafu", "text_ar": "يَزْحَفُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He drags himself along"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] (S, Msb, K)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY AlA^aroDi", "text_ar": "عَلَى الاَرْضِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon the ground"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY", "text_ar": "عَلَى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@sotihi", "text_ar": "ا@سْتِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon his posteriors"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone, said of a child,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he went along slowly, by little and little, upon his posteriors:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd in viii. 15:) and to the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHof", "text_ar": "زَحْف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of children is likened the marching of two bodies of men going to meet each other for fight, when each of them marches gently, or leisurely, towards the other, before they draw near together to smite each other: and one says likewise of a child, before he walks,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY", "text_ar": "عَلَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yatazaH~afu", "text_ar": "يَتَزَحَّفُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA^aroDi", "text_ar": "الاَرْضِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or, as in the T,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY baTonihi", "text_ar": "عَلَى بَطْنِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he drags himself along"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon the ground,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "upon his belly"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa Ald~abaA", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ الدَّبَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The young locusts not yet winged"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "went on,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "forwards:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K:)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ma$aY", "text_ar": "مَشَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in this explanation in the K should be"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maDaY", "text_ar": "مَضَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as in the S and A. (TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "said of an arrow, (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It fell short of the butt, and then slid along to it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * Msb.) ―         -b4-  Also, said of a camel, (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHofN", "text_ar": "زَحْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zuHuwfN", "text_ar": "زُحُوفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafaAnN", "text_ar": "زَحَفَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He became fatigued, and dragged his foot,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the extremity of his foot;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^azoHafu", "text_ar": "اَزْحَفُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, Mgh, Msb:) or this latter signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became fatigued,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and stood still with his master:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raAHilatuhu mina AlA_iEoyaA='i", "text_ar": "رَاحِلَتُهُ مِنَ الاـِعْيَا=ءِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^azoHafato", "text_ar": "اَزْحَفَتْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "His saddle-camel stood still from fatigue:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, accord. to El-Khattábee, correctly,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uzoHifato Ealayohi", "text_ar": "اُزْحِفَتْ عَلَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) or this is a mistake, occurring in the Fáïk; and it is correctly with fet-h: (Mgh:) and accord. to the T,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a camel)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became fatigued, so that he stood still with his master:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or, as some say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "said of one walking, or marching, [i. e., of a man and of a beast,] (Msb, TA,) accord. to AZ, whether fat or lean, (Msb,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHofN", "text_ar": "زَحْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafaAnN", "text_ar": "زَحَفَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or, as AZ says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHofN", "text_ar": "زَحْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zuHuwfN", "text_ar": "زُحُوفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) signifies, (Msb,) or signifies also, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he became fatigued,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, TA,) in walking, or marching. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa Al$~ajaru", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ الشَّجَرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The trees became in a state of gentle motion,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by the influence of the wind. (TA.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHafa Al$~aYo'a", "text_ar": "زَحَفَ الشَّىْءَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaHofN", "text_ar": "زَحْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He dragged the thing along gently."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "Msb", "K", "TK", "T", "TA", "O"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}